{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Plan_Unveiled",
  "title": "A Plan Unveiled",
  "summary": "In a darkened, frigid Sith meditation chamber aboard the Star Destroyer Predator, holding above the dead world of Cochran, Darth Malign convenes his closest advisors to reveal the founding of a new Sith order. The eyeless infiltrator Gillian, the ship's captain Dareus, and the Interdictor commander Axel Vichten are guided by droids onto carved circles beneath red light as Malign unveils his design: a vast underground droid factory hidden beneath the planet's surface, masked by the Dark Side. The advisors press practical concerns, with Dareus warning of the system's barren defenses and Axel detailing the crippling damage to his Interdictor's gravity well generators and the need for repair facilities. Malign assigns Dareus the construction of the droid plant and pledges to requisition a replacement generator from the Empire, then resolves that the brotherhood must steal a space station and drill it into a local asteroid for concealed repairs. The conversation turns to tactics of theft, drilling, and concealment, and as the meeting dissolves the three are dismissed to find their station, exiting back into the light to puzzle over the New Republic's untimely interference at Nar Shaddaa.",
